<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.65.8571.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Photographs and distribution map of Cephalaria anamurensis. A habit and habitat of the type plant B Close-up of flowering capitula C Close-up of fruiting capitula D Distribution of Cephalaria anamurensis (★), Cephalaria elmaliensis (●) and Cephalaria speciosa (■) in Turkey. Photos: Ramazan Sueleyman Goektuerk." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/92593" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.65.8571.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. A Holotype specimen of Cephalaria anamurensis Goektuerk & Suembuel B Reproductive parts of Cephalaria anamurensis (Goektuerk 8018) (1), Cephalaria elmaliensis (Goektuerk 3532) (2) and Cephalaria speciosa (Goektuerk 4727) (3): a corolla b involucral bract c receptacular bract d involucel e calyx." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/92594" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

